reviews.reviewText: The table looks great in the area I needed it. There was one small hiccup with a missing part, but I contacted the company and they immediately got it out to me with no issues. I definitely have no complaints and I really appreciate the great customer service!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I received my set and my first impression was horrible just by judging the packaging that was all beat up. I tried to give it the benefit of the doubt, but after taking it out of the box I realized that a lot of the screws were missing. The instructions gave info to get parts that were missing.Contacted the manufacturer for possible replacement parts, no response. Contacted Amazon and they advised me that I only had the option to return it. Had to try and repackage in an already damaged packaging and return the entire set! Worst experience with Amazon by far!
